1
00:00:27,680 --> 00:00:31,780
♪The moon is shining above
the broken bridge, and the lake ripples♪

2
00:00:31,910 --> 00:00:37,130
♪My heart in a whirl,
with all sorts of feelings♪

3
00:00:37,230 --> 00:00:41,270
♪Clouds encircle the green hills,
and people are in distress♪

4
00:00:41,360 --> 00:00:45,610
♪To help all beings, to be chivalrous♪

5
00:00:46,630 --> 00:00:50,930
♪I wish to ride the wind♪

6
00:00:51,160 --> 00:00:54,960
♪It's never been done♪

7
00:00:56,050 --> 00:01:04,570
♪At this perfect moment,
you wish to exchange♪

8
00:01:05,500 --> 00:01:09,750
♪A thousand of reincarnations
for a lifetime of love♪

9
00:01:10,230 --> 00:01:13,910
♪Watching the fireworks
and the full moon♪

10
00:01:14,890 --> 00:01:19,020
♪With affectionate gaze♪

11
00:01:19,780 --> 00:01:26,710
♪Accumulating lifetimes
of destiny to be with me♪

12
00:01:26,730 --> 00:01:31,550
[Different Princess]

13
00:01:34,100 --> 00:01:36,540
[Episode 22]

14
00:01:37,760 --> 00:01:39,640
[Duke Residence]
Yao hasn't come yet.

15
00:01:39,870 --> 00:01:42,380
[Duke Residence]
She must still resent me as her father.

16
00:01:42,680 --> 00:01:45,230
[Duke Residence]
She must have suffered a lot for years.

17
00:01:45,510 --> 00:01:46,760
If she comes back,

18
00:01:47,000 --> 00:01:48,560
I'll make it up to her double.

19
00:01:49,400 --> 00:01:50,000
Master,

20
00:01:50,920 --> 00:01:52,350
you've been waiting here for days.

21
00:01:52,640 --> 00:01:53,640
You go back to rest first.

22
00:01:54,230 --> 00:01:54,950
I'll inform you

23
00:01:55,200 --> 00:01:56,510
when Young Lady comes back.

24
00:01:57,280 --> 00:01:57,920
By the way,

25
00:01:58,400 --> 00:01:59,430
have you cleaned up

26
00:01:59,640 --> 00:02:00,310
Yao's room?

27
00:02:00,590 --> 00:02:01,400
Yes, I have.

28
00:02:01,870 --> 00:02:03,310
Everything's ready.

29
00:02:04,280 --> 00:02:06,430
Why hasn't Yao come back yet?

30
00:02:07,150 --> 00:02:07,920
Does she not

31
00:02:08,120 --> 00:02:09,800
want to come back to this home?

32
00:02:10,120 --> 00:02:12,000
Young Lady is busy with work,

33
00:02:12,360 --> 00:02:13,750
maybe she'll be back tomorrow.

34
00:02:13,750 --> 00:02:14,430
Master,

35
00:02:14,630 --> 00:02:15,960
you'd better go back to rest first.

36
00:02:20,470 --> 00:02:21,910
Master, Young Lady is back.

37
00:02:22,190 --> 00:02:23,240
Young Lady is back.

38
00:02:29,310 --> 00:02:30,080
Yao,

39
00:02:30,360 --> 00:02:31,310
you're back.

40
00:02:32,120 --> 00:02:33,470
Sorry I'm home late.

41
00:02:33,840 --> 00:02:34,870
You're not late.

42
00:02:35,520 --> 00:02:36,280
Are you hungry?

43
00:02:36,630 --> 00:02:37,280
Come on,

44
00:02:37,470 --> 00:02:38,680
come home with me for dinner.

45
00:02:38,910 --> 00:02:39,680
I saved you

46
00:02:39,910 --> 00:02:41,560
your favourite dumplings.

47
00:02:42,470 --> 00:02:43,430
Okay.

48
00:02:46,520 --> 00:02:47,560
Come on.

49
00:03:00,030 --> 00:03:00,520
Your Highness,

50
00:03:01,520 --> 00:03:02,400
the totem has been drawn.

51
00:03:02,680 --> 00:03:03,310
Please have a look.

52
00:03:53,240 --> 00:03:54,310
How could it be?

53
00:03:57,400 --> 00:03:57,960
Your Highness,

54
00:03:58,680 --> 00:03:59,800
what have you found?

55
00:04:06,030 --> 00:04:06,560
Your Highness,

56
00:04:07,190 --> 00:04:08,840
I've just received
a letter from a pigeon.

57
00:04:09,360 --> 00:04:10,000
It's reported

58
00:04:10,360 --> 00:04:11,240
that Du Hui

59
00:04:11,590 --> 00:04:12,680
was once a famous young talent

60
00:04:12,680 --> 00:04:13,190
in Fuyu,

61
00:04:13,590 --> 00:04:14,280
good at literature and martial arts.

62
00:04:14,960 --> 00:04:15,630
He became

63
00:04:15,870 --> 00:04:17,270
a third-ranked official
when he was still young.

64
00:04:18,160 --> 00:04:18,830
But then,

65
00:04:19,120 --> 00:04:20,750
without any reason, he resigned

66
00:04:21,000 --> 00:04:22,240
and vanished into thin air.

67
00:04:23,430 --> 00:04:24,600
Did anything big happen in Fuyu

68
00:04:25,040 --> 00:04:26,240
the year Du Hui resigned?

69
00:04:26,510 --> 00:04:27,240
Yes.

70
00:04:27,800 --> 00:04:29,240
Firstly, Fuyu surrendered to Liang.

71
00:04:29,830 --> 00:04:30,870
Secondly...

72
00:04:31,240 --> 00:04:31,870
What's it?

73
00:04:32,360 --> 00:04:34,560
The empress married to Liang.

74
00:04:37,760 --> 00:04:40,570
[East Office]

75
00:04:46,000 --> 00:04:46,480
Yes.

76
00:04:53,310 --> 00:04:53,870
Your Highness,

77
00:04:54,190 --> 00:04:55,360
it's all been arranged.

78
00:04:57,240 --> 00:04:58,240
No matter what,

79
00:04:59,390 --> 00:05:00,190
I can't let my mother

80
00:05:00,310 --> 00:05:01,270
appear to the public

81
00:05:01,430 --> 00:05:02,680
like this.

82
00:05:13,600 --> 00:05:16,510
Red Luan Constellation Signs
are never alone.

83
00:05:17,040 --> 00:05:18,240
They always appear in pairs.

84
00:05:19,560 --> 00:05:20,600
And on whose body

85
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:23,240
is its other half engraved?

86
00:05:26,950 --> 00:05:28,800
It all started 20 years ago.

87
00:05:30,630 --> 00:05:31,870
When I was young and ignorant,

88
00:05:32,070 --> 00:05:33,040
I was in love with a rich girl

89
00:05:33,240 --> 00:05:34,390
but I couldn't be with her.

90
00:05:35,310 --> 00:05:37,310
So, I traveled to Liang
to seek a new life.

91
00:05:42,950 --> 00:05:44,120
Why don't you let me

92
00:05:44,160 --> 00:05:45,360
reconstruct the story for you?

93
00:05:47,120 --> 00:05:48,160
Twenty years ago,

94
00:05:49,390 --> 00:05:51,040
you were an official in Fuyu.

95
00:05:52,190 --> 00:05:54,430
You were in love with a young lady
from a prestigious family.

96
00:05:55,920 --> 00:05:57,240
The two of you were
so in love with each other

97
00:05:57,430 --> 00:05:58,560
that you committed yourself
to each other.

98
00:06:00,630 --> 00:06:02,600
But because of your different status,

99
00:06:02,680 --> 00:06:04,240
you had to be separated.

100
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:10,040
Then, the young lady
married far away to Liang.

101
00:06:10,920 --> 00:06:12,160
You couldn't let go of her,

102
00:06:12,830 --> 00:06:13,430
so you resigned

103
00:06:13,600 --> 00:06:15,070
from your post
as a third-ranked official

104
00:06:15,600 --> 00:06:17,070
and followed her to Liang

105
00:06:17,240 --> 00:06:18,560
as a secretary.

106
00:06:24,920 --> 00:06:26,750
It's hard for me

107
00:06:27,390 --> 00:06:28,480
not to think of

108
00:06:28,680 --> 00:06:31,240
the third princess of Fuyu

109
00:06:32,600 --> 00:06:35,000
and now the empress of Liang,

110
00:06:35,190 --> 00:06:37,510
both from Fuyu with high status

111
00:06:38,190 --> 00:06:40,240
and of the same age,

112
00:06:40,920 --> 00:06:44,040
that's Hua Yunni.

113
00:06:52,480 --> 00:06:53,800
Stop kidding around, Your Highness.

114
00:06:55,070 --> 00:06:56,270
The empress is so noble.

115
00:06:57,430 --> 00:06:58,950
Is she accessible to mediocre people

116
00:06:58,950 --> 00:07:00,160
like me?

117
00:07:01,800 --> 00:07:03,310
You fell in love

118
00:07:03,310 --> 00:07:05,750
with the empress when you were young,

119
00:07:06,390 --> 00:07:08,510
and now you're willingly sent by her

120
00:07:10,190 --> 00:07:11,800
to murder Prince Qi.

121
00:07:12,310 --> 00:07:13,190
Your Highness,

122
00:07:16,000 --> 00:07:17,160
the guards at the gate report

123
00:07:17,240 --> 00:07:17,870
that Princess Consort Lv is here.

124
00:07:18,070 --> 00:07:19,240
Should we let her see Du Hui?

125
00:07:38,920 --> 00:07:40,190
Secretary Du promised to give it to you.

126
00:07:41,830 --> 00:07:43,600
Don't let anyone know about this.

127
00:07:53,630 --> 00:07:54,390
Why did you

128
00:07:54,830 --> 00:07:56,040
call me here?

129
00:07:57,480 --> 00:07:58,310
Miss Qing,

130
00:07:59,240 --> 00:08:01,070
I do have a favour to ask of you.

131
00:08:02,510 --> 00:08:04,240
You're Yunni's real niece.

132
00:08:05,070 --> 00:08:06,160
Please do me a favour

133
00:08:06,680 --> 00:08:08,270
by delivering a message.

134
00:08:09,270 --> 00:08:10,070
Why does Du Hui

135
00:08:10,240 --> 00:08:11,870
want to ask Qing to deliver a message?

136
00:08:14,000 --> 00:08:15,310
Walls have ears.

137
00:08:28,120 --> 00:08:28,800
Help!

138
00:08:29,070 --> 00:08:30,000
Guards!

139
00:08:30,600 --> 00:08:31,510
Come here!

140
00:08:34,270 --> 00:08:35,030
Stay away.

141
00:08:36,200 --> 00:08:37,510
Put out the fire.

142
00:08:37,750 --> 00:08:38,240
Yes.

143
00:09:19,770 --> 00:09:20,550
Phosphorus powder?

144
00:09:48,120 --> 00:09:50,600
[Zhaochun Pavilion]

145
00:09:52,870 --> 00:09:53,550
Yun.

146
00:10:02,030 --> 00:10:03,390
Sometimes, it's wonderful not to be able

147
00:10:04,270 --> 00:10:06,030
to be with your loved ones.

148
00:10:10,200 --> 00:10:11,080
What's wrong, Yun?

149
00:10:11,670 --> 00:10:13,120
What's with

150
00:10:13,390 --> 00:10:14,600
the frown?

151
00:10:16,440 --> 00:10:17,240
Leave us alone.

152
00:10:29,670 --> 00:10:31,120
I remember when I was a child,

153
00:10:31,960 --> 00:10:32,600
I saw a mark

154
00:10:32,600 --> 00:10:34,600
on your body by accident.

155
00:10:39,030 --> 00:10:40,320
You also said it was
when you were a child.

156
00:10:40,840 --> 00:10:42,240
It makes sense that your memory

157
00:10:42,360 --> 00:10:43,240
would be off.

158
00:10:43,360 --> 00:10:43,960
You know

159
00:10:44,120 --> 00:10:45,510
I'm not a rash person.

160
00:10:46,000 --> 00:10:47,960
Since I recognised the totem,

161
00:10:49,120 --> 00:10:50,390
I can't be wrong.

162
00:10:56,320 --> 00:10:56,960
If you want me

163
00:10:57,120 --> 00:10:58,390
to admit that I have the totem,

164
00:11:00,320 --> 00:11:01,670
I will.

165
00:11:03,240 --> 00:11:04,550
If I'm not mistaken,

166
00:11:06,120 --> 00:11:07,510
the totem is

167
00:11:07,670 --> 00:11:08,870
the life and death pact of Fuyu,

168
00:11:10,080 --> 00:11:11,510
Red Luan Constellation Signs.

169
00:11:12,240 --> 00:11:14,240
As a half-Fuyu,

170
00:11:15,030 --> 00:11:16,600
I know a bit about it.

171
00:11:17,120 --> 00:11:18,750
Then, what do you want to know

172
00:11:19,270 --> 00:11:20,270
from me today?

173
00:11:20,790 --> 00:11:22,840
I want you to tell me the truth.

174
00:11:23,270 --> 00:11:24,510
What is your relationship

175
00:11:24,870 --> 00:11:26,550
with Du Hui?

176
00:11:41,120 --> 00:11:42,150
I saw Du Hui

177
00:11:43,630 --> 00:11:45,080
buy this ornament

178
00:11:45,080 --> 00:11:47,240
at the Mid-Autumn Festival Fair.

179
00:11:49,320 --> 00:11:50,840
Do you still not want to admit it?

180
00:11:54,550 --> 00:11:56,630
The life and death pact
between you and Du Hui

181
00:11:57,080 --> 00:11:58,270
means that you were already

182
00:11:58,440 --> 00:11:59,870
in love with him

183
00:12:00,030 --> 00:12:01,960
before you married Father.

184
00:12:02,910 --> 00:12:04,080
Is that the case?

185
00:12:13,030 --> 00:12:14,000
So you're the one

186
00:12:15,870 --> 00:12:18,440
who ordered Du Hui
to stay in East Office

187
00:12:19,120 --> 00:12:20,630
for so many years.

188
00:12:22,960 --> 00:12:24,320
He was your subordinate,

189
00:12:25,630 --> 00:12:27,390
and served you with all his heart.

190
00:12:29,320 --> 00:12:31,960
I didn't expect Ji Chu
to take over East Office,

191
00:12:32,670 --> 00:12:35,600
so he had another role to play.

192
00:12:36,200 --> 00:12:37,270
Did you order Du Hui

193
00:12:37,480 --> 00:12:39,360
to kill Feng?

194
00:12:53,200 --> 00:12:54,240
So,

195
00:12:57,360 --> 00:12:59,440
you've always taught me

196
00:13:00,480 --> 00:13:01,840
to be generous,

197
00:13:02,480 --> 00:13:03,870
kind and courteous.

198
00:13:05,510 --> 00:13:06,670
Now,

199
00:13:08,240 --> 00:13:09,870
does that still stand?

200
00:13:12,200 --> 00:13:13,080
Yun.

201
00:13:22,240 --> 00:13:23,600
I remember when I was little,

202
00:13:25,320 --> 00:13:26,600
you punished me to copy

203
00:13:26,840 --> 00:13:28,120
the sutra a hundred times

204
00:13:31,750 --> 00:13:34,150
because I snatched
a piece of cake with Chu.

205
00:13:34,440 --> 00:13:35,390
You told me

206
00:13:36,120 --> 00:13:38,080
not to fight

207
00:13:38,750 --> 00:13:40,910
with my brother,

208
00:13:41,630 --> 00:13:43,840
and to give in when I could.

209
00:13:44,760 --> 00:13:46,760
[Zhaochun Pavilion]

210
00:13:49,910 --> 00:13:52,630
You influenced me not to fight

211
00:13:54,670 --> 00:13:56,670
and not to compete for anything.

212
00:14:00,000 --> 00:14:01,120
So,

213
00:14:03,080 --> 00:14:05,240
it's true

214
00:14:05,630 --> 00:14:08,030
what you've taught me?

215
00:14:35,530 --> 00:14:38,450
[Jinglv Hall]

216
00:14:47,510 --> 00:14:49,000
Why don't you ask me

217
00:14:49,120 --> 00:14:50,600
why I went to see Du Hui?

218
00:15:00,360 --> 00:15:01,080
After all, I'm

219
00:15:01,080 --> 00:15:02,440
the empress's real niece.

220
00:15:02,630 --> 00:15:03,240
Aren't you afraid that I'll...

221
00:15:03,360 --> 00:15:04,030
Alright, Qing.

222
00:15:08,240 --> 00:15:08,790
I trust you.

223
00:15:13,150 --> 00:15:13,960
Ji Chu.

224
00:15:15,080 --> 00:15:16,550
Tell me what just

225
00:15:16,550 --> 00:15:17,360
happened.

226
00:15:19,750 --> 00:15:20,440
Why did you

227
00:15:20,750 --> 00:15:21,910
call me here?

228
00:15:24,550 --> 00:15:25,200
Miss Qing,

229
00:15:25,840 --> 00:15:27,440
I do have a favour to ask of you.

230
00:15:29,240 --> 00:15:30,750
You're Yunni's real niece.

231
00:15:31,630 --> 00:15:33,030
Please do me a favour

232
00:15:33,790 --> 00:15:35,550
by delivering a message.

233
00:15:36,600 --> 00:15:37,150
So I

234
00:15:38,150 --> 00:15:40,120
won't have regrets in my life.

235
00:15:40,840 --> 00:15:42,390
Besides, 15 years ago...

236
00:15:45,320 --> 00:15:46,390
Guards!

237
00:15:52,270 --> 00:15:52,790
Your Highness,

238
00:15:53,750 --> 00:15:55,000
this person was caught outside the jail

239
00:15:55,200 --> 00:15:56,750
using a bronze mirror
to reflect the light.

240
00:15:59,270 --> 00:16:02,080
You're the one who sprinkled
the phosphorus powder

241
00:16:02,320 --> 00:16:03,480
on the withered grass
and Du Hui, aren't you?

242
00:16:07,910 --> 00:16:08,670
And this.

243
00:16:18,960 --> 00:16:22,390
It seems that you've been feuding
with Du Hui for a long time.

244
00:16:24,000 --> 00:16:25,360
Even if he wasn't in jail,

245
00:16:25,630 --> 00:16:26,910
I'd still have to kill him

246
00:16:27,120 --> 00:16:27,910
somehow.

247
00:16:29,840 --> 00:16:30,440
Take him away.

248
00:16:30,600 --> 00:16:31,240
Yes.

249
00:16:31,630 --> 00:16:32,320
Take him away.

250
00:16:42,360 --> 00:16:43,440
So much was written?

251
00:16:46,360 --> 00:16:47,550
It's just a false impression

252
00:16:48,000 --> 00:16:50,030
that the murderer was bullied
by Du Hui all these years.

253
00:16:52,080 --> 00:16:53,840
Du Hui had a good reputation
in East Office

254
00:16:54,320 --> 00:16:55,480
all these years.

255
00:16:57,860 --> 00:16:59,420
This is an absolute falsehood.

256
00:16:59,870 --> 00:17:00,480
Someone wants us

257
00:17:00,480 --> 00:17:02,030
to close the case of Ji Feng soon.

258
00:17:04,160 --> 00:17:06,070
But who got the assassin

259
00:17:06,240 --> 00:17:07,160
to kill Du Hui?

260
00:17:07,400 --> 00:17:08,160
Who do you think

261
00:17:08,510 --> 00:17:10,960
is most eager to shut Du Hui up?

262
00:17:15,790 --> 00:17:16,640
Do you remember

263
00:17:16,640 --> 00:17:18,160
the message Du Hui asked you to deliver?

264
00:17:19,760 --> 00:17:21,590
[Fengyi Palace]

265
00:17:24,200 --> 00:17:25,240
These things

266
00:17:26,750 --> 00:17:28,960
have been with me for years.

267
00:17:32,310 --> 00:17:33,350
Pin Yan,

268
00:17:35,030 --> 00:17:36,200
do you think time

269
00:17:37,000 --> 00:17:39,070
has changed everything?

270
00:17:41,160 --> 00:17:41,790
Your Highness,

271
00:17:42,400 --> 00:17:44,790
these things may be yellow and worn,

272
00:17:45,240 --> 00:17:46,240
but they're still here

273
00:17:46,400 --> 00:17:48,240
with you.

274
00:17:50,350 --> 00:17:52,070
Do you remember this hairpin?

275
00:17:54,000 --> 00:17:55,000
Yes, I do.

276
00:17:55,880 --> 00:17:56,880
This is the only thing

277
00:17:58,350 --> 00:18:00,510
that connects me to him.

278
00:18:04,000 --> 00:18:04,680
Your Highness!

279
00:18:12,240 --> 00:18:14,350
Princess Consort Lv has arrived.

280
00:18:33,510 --> 00:18:34,070
Aunt.

281
00:18:34,310 --> 00:18:35,030
Qing,

282
00:18:35,830 --> 00:18:37,640
why did you come
to the palace at this hour?

283
00:18:39,270 --> 00:18:40,640
Let's sit down and talk.

284
00:18:41,270 --> 00:18:42,240
Okay.

285
00:18:51,830 --> 00:18:55,070
There's something I need to tell you.

286
00:18:56,750 --> 00:18:57,480
What's it?

287
00:19:02,590 --> 00:19:05,310
Yesterday, I sneaked into the jail

288
00:19:05,550 --> 00:19:06,590
to see Du Hui.

289
00:19:13,550 --> 00:19:14,640
Du Hui?

290
00:19:17,790 --> 00:19:19,830
