346
00:23:08,400 --> 00:23:10,110
If you keep looking at me, I'll
take it as a sign that you like me.

347
00:23:10,110 --> 00:23:12,730
♪My heart in a whirl,
with all sorts of feelings♪

348
00:23:12,730 --> 00:23:16,610
