421
00:26:21,350 --> 00:26:22,550
That's true,

422
00:26:23,480 --> 00:26:25,310
but I've learned about

423
00:26:26,000 --> 00:26:28,440
your ambition from

424
00:26:28,640 --> 00:26:30,200
