as a bargaining chip?

444
00:27:18,160 --> 00:27:19,070
That's not true.

445
00:27:20,510 --> 00:27:22,680
Yao is my beloved daughter.

446
00:27:23,070 --> 00:27:24,830
I just want her

447
00:27:25,000 --> 00:27:26,070
