448
00:27:27,070 --> 00:27:30,200
So if my daughter marries you,

449
00:27:31,510 --> 00:27:35,400
I want her to be Princess Consort Lv.

450
00:27:36,310 --> 00:27:38,240
He's making me give away my position?

451
00:27:39,270 --> 00:27:40,750
However, I'm not good enough

452
00:27:40,920 --> 00:27:43,200
