456
00:27:54,030 --> 00:27:54,960
Why?

457
00:27:56,640 --> 00:27:59,240
I already have a wife.

458
00:28:00,270 --> 00:28:01,790
Ji Chu gave up

459
00:28:02,160 --> 00:28:04,160
