466
00:28:50,590 --> 00:28:51,640
such a good opportunity

467
00:28:52,030 --> 00:28:53,350
to get Duke's support?

468
00:29:08,160 --> 00:29:09,960
I won't do anything

469
00:29:10,880 --> 00:29:12,270
